  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">ECHO- IREACH - Inclusive Rapid Emergency Humanitarian Assistance in West Bengal affected by cyclone</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Through IREACH project we are supporting Cyclone Amphan affected communities with-
- Unconditional Cash Transfer
- Water Sanitation and Hygiene 
- Conditional Cash Transfer for House repair

This project is the continuation of earlier project and in view of the change in programme objective new project was created to process the balance grant.  The project proposal &amp; budget are attached in the project link given below.

ECHO- IREACH - Inclusive Rapid Emergency Humanitarian Assistance in West Bengal affected by
&lt;http://promiselive.caid.local/ChristianAid/userdefined/edit.aspx?id=%7b7C325C76-ADA4-EA11-AE84-005056BE001C%7d&amp;_CreateFromType=1&amp;_CreateFromId=%7b06B1D162-16F4-E011-BE9E-005056BE001C%7d&amp;etc=10000#&gt;

This is a monitoring cost which has been moved to partner budget.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Water/sanitation hygiene to inculcate best practices and save the lives of people from water borne disease.  Conditional transfer to give community a liberty to invest for essential work and conditional repair work to ensure strengthening of construction and also resilience to withstand disaster.</narrative>
  </description>
